devicefields.name: SETTINGS_ID
devicefields.note: Well-known value. Uniquely identifies this as a sunspec model settings (121)

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_L
devicefields.note: Length of sunspec model settings (121)

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_WMax
devicefields.note: Setting for maximum power output. Default to WRtg.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VRef
devicefields.note: Voltage at the PCC.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VRefOfs
devicefields.note: Offset  from PCC to inverter.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VMax
devicefields.note: Setpoint for maximum voltage.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VMin
devicefields.note: Setpoint for minimum voltage.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VAMax
devicefields.note: Setpoint for maximum apparent power. Default to VARtg.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VArMaxQ1
devicefields.note: Setting for maximum reactive power in quadrant 1. Default to VArRtgQ1.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VArMaxQ2
devicefields.note: Setting for maximum reactive power in quadrant 2. Default to VArRtgQ2.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VArMaxQ3
devicefields.note: Setting for maximum reactive power in quadrant 3. Default to VArRtgQ3.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VArMaxQ4
devicefields.note: Setting for maximum reactive power in quadrant 4. Default to VArRtgQ4.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_WGra
devicefields.note: Default ramp rate of change of active power due to command or internal action.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_PFMinQ1
devicefields.note: Setpoint for minimum power factor value in quadrant 1. Default to PFRtgQ1.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_PFMinQ2
devicefields.note: Setpoint for minimum power factor value in quadrant 2. Default to PFRtgQ2.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_PFMinQ3
devicefields.note: Setpoint for minimum power factor value in quadrant 3. Default to PFRtgQ3.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_PFMinQ4
devicefields.note: Setpoint for minimum power factor value in quadrant 4. Default to PFRtgQ4.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VArAct
devicefields.note: VAR action on change between charging and discharging: 1=switch 2=maintain VAR characterization.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_ClcTotVA
devicefields.note: Calculation method for total apparent power. 1=vector 2=arithmetic.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_MaxRmpRte
devicefields.note: Setpoint for maximum ramp rate as percentage of nominal maximum ramp rate. This setting will limit the rate that watts delivery to the grid can increase or decrease in response to intermittent PV generation.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_ECPNomHz
devicefields.note: Setpoint for nominal frequency at the ECP.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_ConnPh
devicefields.note: Identity of connected phase for single phase inverters. A=1 B=2 C=3.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_WMax_SF
devicefields.note: Scale factor for real power.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VRef_SF
devicefields.note: Scale factor for voltage at the PCC.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VRefOfs_SF
devicefields.note: Scale factor for offset voltage.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VMinMax_SF
devicefields.note: Scale factor for min/max voltages.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VAMax_SF
devicefields.note: Scale factor for apparent power.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_VArMax_SF
devicefields.note: Scale factor for reactive power.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_WGra_SF
devicefields.note: Scale factor for default ramp rate.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_PFMin_SF
devicefields.note: Scale factor for minimum power factor.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_MaxRmpRte_SF
devicefields.note: Scale factor for maximum ramp percentage.

devicefields.name: SETTINGS_ECPNomHz_SF
devicefields.note: Scale factor for nominal frequency.
